    <title>Women and Girls contributor: Sara Hylton</title>
    <description>Sara Hylton is currently based between Brooklyn, New York, and New Delhi, and covers women’s issues and human rights. Her principal medium is the portrait. Resilience, humanity and the quiet beauty in everyday life guides her work and the stories she covers. Follow her work on her website and on Instagram.
 
 
